# FreightFlow — Happy-Path Walkthrough
# VS Code REST Client — run each request with Ctrl+Alt+R
# Full sequence implemented in Milestone 5; health checks usable from Milestone 0.
#
# All requests go through the Gateway on port 8080.
# For direct-service testing during development, swap 8080 for 5000/5001/5002.

@gateway = http://localhost:8080

# ─── Milestone 0: Health checks ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### RFP API health
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Carrier API health
GET http://localhost:5001/health

### Workflow Worker health
GET http://localhost:5002/health

### Gateway health
GET http://localhost:8080/health


# ─── Milestone 5: Full happy path (fill in after Milestone 5) ──────────────────

### 1. Get a JWT (local dev stub — not a real auth server)
# POST {{gateway}}/token
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "sub": "shipper-1",
#   "role": "shipper"
# }

### 2. Onboard a carrier
# @token = <paste token from step 1>
# POST {{gateway}}/carriers
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "dotNumber": "1234567",
#   "name": "Acme Trucking LLC",
#   "insuranceExpiry": "2027-12-31"
# }

### 3. Create an RFP
# POST {{gateway}}/rfps
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "shipperId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
#   "maxBidRounds": 3,
#   "openAt": "2026-05-01T00:00:00Z",
#   "closeAt": "2026-05-15T00:00:00Z"
# }

### 4. Add a lane
# POST {{gateway}}/rfps/{{rfpId}}/lanes
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "originZip": "90210",
#   "destZip": "10001",
#   "freightClass": "Class70",
#   "volume": 100
# }

### 5. Open the RFP
# POST {{gateway}}/rfps/{{rfpId}}/open
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Submit a bid
# POST {{gateway}}/rfps/{{rfpId}}/bids
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Idempotency-Key: bid-key-001
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "carrierId": "{{carrierId}}",
#   "lanePrices": [
#     { "laneId": "{{laneId}}", "amount": 1250.00, "currency": "USD" }
#   ]
# }

### 7. Award the carrier
# POST {{gateway}}/rfps/{{rfpId}}/awards
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# { "bidId": "{{bidId}}" }

### 8. Get RFP state
# GET {{gateway}}/rfps/{{rfpId}}
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
